8: Looks like Vivi is in high spirits today.
12:
Indeed! It helps that there aren't any
unwanted visitors looking for her in
this world.
18:
Hey, Vivi, I don't mind the company...
But could you maybe give me some
more space?
23:
S-sorry... It's just that your back is
so... Perfect...
26:
It's so cute and defenseless... I could
just about stab you at any minute!
Hehe.
29:
Why do I feel like you're only
half-joking...
34:
Heh, come on, there's nothing to
worry about. It sounds like she's "got
your back", after all.
40:
Oh my! Who is this beautiful little
thing?! Is this a goddess I see in my
midst?!
42:
Hey pretty girl, how about getting
some dumplings with yours truly?!
46:
S-sorry, it's nothing personal! I-I just
get so startled when somebody
approaches me like that...
50:
...Wait a minute, there's something
odd about you...
52:
...Looks like there's more to you than
meets the eye.
55:
Reveal yourself, ninja! Who is your
master?!
57:
Playing dumb, are we? Then I'll wring
that answer out of you, one way or
another!
63: Are you also trying to recruit me?
69:
Stop lying! Just when I thought I had
gotten away from that assassin, I
get pulled into another mess in this
world.
74:
Such uncanny movements... Just
who are you, exactly?!
76:
Please... S-stop staring at me like
that...
87: ...That should do it. I think we lost him.
97:
Don't worry about it. It looks like that
guy confused you with a ninja.
Nobody to blame except for our bad
luck.
101:
But damn, Vivi, that was some good
stuff. You got behind that guy like it
was nothing!
108:
It's why the assassin targeted me in
the first place...
111:
Maybe he was right... Maybe my
abilities are only good for hurting
people!
116:
The hell they are! It all depends on
how you use 'em.
122:
I do admit that it gets a little scary
when you pop up behind me...
124:
But you've never hurt anyone before,
right? That's what makes you
different from that assassin.
129:
You are an adventurer. Not an
assassin.
134:
*sniff* Thank you... Thank you so
much!
138:
What's with that face? We're only
stating the obvious!
143:
But... Oh no, you're all staring at me!
P-please...
148: Ahhh! There we go... Much better...
151:
Um. You're... Welcome? What's going
on...
155:
Don't look so worried, Nimbus! She's
"got your back", remember?
165: I still prefer your back, Alk...
167:
It's perfect. Vulnerable and easy to
hide behind... It's almost like a
second home to me... Hehe.
171:
What sort of home did you grow up
in?!
174:
Could we try establishing some...
ground rules from now on?
178:
...Yes, we can. I'll do my best. I'm an
adventurer, after all!
180:
...Who just so happens to like
sneaking up behind people... Hehe.
